 288:..\..\..\HamFlyAPI\src/hamfly_core_telemetry.c **** // off 11-12 BE int16: IMU rate (mirrors attr 1 off 11-12).
 289:..\..\..\HamFlyAPI\src/hamfly_core_telemetry.c **** // off 13    always 0x00.
